<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HAWITHA KA HMUH CANG CH355</title>
<key>A</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Keimah nih hawitha ka hmuh cang, Ka hngalh hlan in a ka dawt, Dawtnak
 hri in a ka hnuh i, Khi hri in a ka tem dih Ka lungthin kha a ka tem i,
 Ho hmanh nih an phoih kho lo, Ka ta a si, a ta ka si, Zungzal in zungzal
 tiangin.

[V2]
 Keimah nih hawitha ka hmuh cang, Keimah khamh awkah a thi, Nunnak kha
 a ka pek hleiah, A pum tiang zong a ka pek, Keimah ta zeihmanh a um lo,
 Ka Bawipa ta a si dih, Ka thazang, nunnak, ka zeizong, Amah nih a pen
 zungzal.

[V3]
 Keimah nih hawitha ka hmuh cang, Sunparnak kha a ka pek, Vancung lam i
 ka kal lioah, Inntha chungah a ka hruai, A zungzal a lianh-ngannak nih, A
 ka bawmtu a si cang, Ruahchan nak in ka tuan lai i, Hnangam in ka um te
 lai.

[V4]
 Keimah nih hawitha ka hmuh cang, A ka hramh i a ka dawt, Fimnak lam
 kha a ka hmuhsak, Bochan awkah a tha fawn, Khi tluk a ka dawmi sinin,
 Zeidah a ka then kho lai, Nunnak, thihnak, hrem hmun nih maw, Then hlah a
 ta ka si ko.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>355</hymn_number>
</song>